<div class="fy_zcbj">

    <div class="fy_sqw">
    	<h3>陕西省中医医院第三方陪护服务项目竞争性磋商公告</h3>
      <i>发布时间：2025-07-25 09:22   来源：   浏览次数：<script type='text/javascript' src='/web/news_checknum.rt?contentId=15272&channlId=278'></script></i>
       
        <div style="color:#000000;">
      		<p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">项目名称：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">陕西省中医医院第三方陪护服务项目</span></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">采购方式：竞争性磋商</span></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">采购需求：为进一步维护我院的利益和声誉，提高我院服务质量</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">　　一、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">信息</span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名时间：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">5</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">7月24</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">日至</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">20</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">25</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">31</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">日</span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">每日上午</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">8:30至11:00，下午14:30至17:00，节假日除外</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">）</span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">报名地点：莲湖区西华门大街</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">17号莲湖区图书馆陕西省中医医院行政办公区</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">公告期限：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2025年7月31日</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">投标及开标信息</span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">投标截止时间：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2025年8月5日上午9点整（北京时间）</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">开标时间：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2025年8月5日上午9点整（北京时间）</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">开标地点：陕西省中医医院行政办公区一楼</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">114</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名要求：</span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">供应商需提供以下资格审查必备文件：</span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">1、营业执照或身份证明：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">供应商合法注册的法人或其他组织的营业执照等证明文件，自然人的身份证明；</span> </span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">2、授权委托书：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">供应商参加本项目的合法授权人授权委托书；</span> </span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">供应商应授权合法的人员参加响应全过程，其中法定代表人直接参加的，须出具法人身份证，并与营业执照上信息一致。法定代表人授权代表参加的，须出具法定代表人授权书及授权代表身份证；</span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">3、财务状况证明：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">2023年度以来（任意1年）审计报告或近3个月内出具的银行资信证明；</span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">4、缴纳税收和社会保障资金证明：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">投标截止前</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">6个月内任意1个月缴纳税收和社会保障金的缴费凭据（打印件，加盖单位公章）；依法不需要缴纳的供应商应提供相关文件证明；</span></span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">5、无违法记录声明：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">投标人应出具参加本次政府采购活动前</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">3年内在经营活动中无重大违法记录,以及未被列入失信被执行人、重大税收违法案件当事人名单、政府采购严重违法失信行为记录的书面声明；</span></span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">6、特定资格：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">投标人须具备专业陪护服务公司资质。</span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">以上为资格审查必备资质。磋商时，根据供应商提供的上述资格证明文件进行资格审查，未通过资格审查的，其响应文件将按无效响应处理。（供应商须提供资格证明文件原件备查）</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;line-height: 23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">　　本项目不接受联合体。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">四、联系人：赵老师　联系电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">029-87251591</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-right:7px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:right;line-height:23px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">陕西省中医医院资产管理办公室</span></p><p style="text-indent: 400px; text-align: right; line-height: 23px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">5</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">24</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">日</span></p><p><br/></p>
      	</div>
    </div>


</div>


